div.p:
But how if neither of the former I can challenge to my ſelf; 
                  Queſt. 
                but all that I have had to deal withall have been carnall men, what may I do in ſuch a caſe to get within the Covenant?

I confeſſe then thy condition is ſo much the more to be pitied; 
                  Anſw. 
                but ſeeing we were not born free, wee muſt therefore take a courſe whereby wee may become free.
